<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire is not typically an important disturbance factor; the alliance usually occurs on open slopes or in meadows adjacent to riparian settings and forests.</div>
